WEBVTT

00:03:59.832 --> 00:04:04.971
This looks at how to use design
to create positive change in the world.

00:04:06.209 --> 00:04:07.630
While I was there,

00:04:07.654 --> 00:04:09.471
I fell in love with woodworking.

00:04:10.217 --> 00:04:12.914
But what I quickly realized

00:04:12.938 --> 00:04:15.382
was that I was missing out on something.

00:04:16.058 --> 00:04:18.997
As you're working with a tool,

00:04:19.021 --> 00:04:21.450
right before it's about
to kick back at you --

00:04:21.474 --> 00:04:24.733
which means the piece or the tool
jumps back at you --

00:04:24.757 --> 00:04:25.923
it makes a sound.

00:04:26.992 --> 00:04:28.582
And I couldn't hear this sound.

